node.title: Natalie Wood
node.description: A look at the actress' career, from child star to her untimely and mysterious death
node.content: ["In November 2011, the Los Angeles County Sheriff's Department re-opened its investigation in the death of actress Natalie Wood nearly 30 years after the actress drowned in the waters off Southern California. It is one of Hollywood's most enduring mysteries. \u00a0", "More than 36 years after her death, investigators spoke to \"48 Hours\" about what they\u00a0learned.\u00a0"]
